Access Media Group also known as AMG ( formerly known as Learning & Skills Television of Alberta Ltd. ) is a privately held Canadian broadcasting and multimedia company based in Edmonton , Alberta , Canada specializing in learning - based media . It owns four television stations , a multimedia distribution company , and a school for continuing education and personal growth . At the time of the company 's founding in 1994 , it was 60 % owned by CHUM Limited . On February 15 2005 CHUM purchased the remainder of the company and rebranded the company 's name as Access Media Group . AMG also organizes ideaCity , an annual conference of forward - thinkers held in Toronto . Animal Planet • BNN • BookTelevision • Bravo ! . Some of the assets listed above are only partially owned by CTVglobemedia . Refer to full asset list for detailed information . 